DefaultType
[Stereotype]




Description: This stereotype tells Rhapsody what is the DefaultType when creating a new term element based on 'Part' or 'Variable'.
The user will add to the new term a dependency (with the 'DefaultType' stereotype) on a certain Model Element type, which will be the default type upon creation of the new term element. For example see 'ProxyPort' in the SysML profile.
OfMetaClass: Dependency
